trans-unit.source: dRuby allows methods to be called in one Ruby process upon a Ruby object located in another Ruby process, even on another machine. References to objects can be passed between processes. Method arguments and return values are dumped and loaded in marshalled format. All of this is done transparently to both the caller of the remote method and the object that it is called upon.
trans-unit.target: dRuby允许在位于另一个Ruby进程（甚至在另一台机器上）中的Ruby对象上的一个Ruby进程中调用方法。可以在进程之间传递对对象的引用。 Method 参数和返回值以编组格式转储并加载。所有这些对于远程方法的调用者和被调用的对象都是透明的。

trans-unit.source: dRuby calls made into a process are handled by a DRb::DRbServer instance within that process. This reconstitutes the method call, invokes it upon the specified local object, and returns the value to the remote caller. Any object can receive calls over dRuby. There is no need to implement a special interface, or mixin special functionality. Nor, in the general case, does an object need to explicitly register itself with a DRbServer in order to receive dRuby calls.
trans-unit.target: 对进程的dRuby调用由该进程中的DRb::DRbServer实例处理。这将重构方法调用,在指定的本地对象上调用它,并将值返回给远程调用者。任何对象都可以通过dRuby接收调用。不需要实现一个特殊的接口,或者混入特殊的功能。在一般情况下,一个对象也不需要为了接收dRuby调用而明确地将自己注册到DRbServer中。
客户端/服务器模式下的dRuby

trans-unit.source: dRuby is a distributed object system for Ruby. It is written in pure Ruby and uses its own protocol. No add-in services are needed beyond those provided by the Ruby runtime, such as TCP sockets. It does not rely on or interoperate with other distributed object systems such as CORBA, RMI, or .NET.
trans-unit.target: dRuby是一个Ruby的分布式对象系统。它是用纯Ruby编写的,使用自己的协议。除了Ruby运行时提供的服务,如TCP套接字,不需要任何附加服务。它不依赖于或与其他分布式对象系统(如CORBA、RMI或.NET)互操作。

trans-unit.source: dRuby is implemented using three main components: a remote method call marshaller/unmarshaller; a transport protocol; and an ID-to-object mapper. The latter two can be directly, and the first indirectly, replaced, in order to provide different behaviour and capabilities.
trans-unit.target: dRuby使用三个主要组件来实现:一个远程方法调用marshaller/unmarshaller;一个传输协议;一个ID到对象的映射器。后两个可以直接替换,第一个可以间接替换,以提供不同的行为和功能。

trans-unit.source: dRuby supports calling remote methods with blocks. As blocks (or rather the Proc objects that represent them) are not marshallable, the block executes in the local, not the remote, context. Each value yielded to the block is passed from the remote object to the local block, then the value returned by each block invocation is passed back to the remote execution context to be collected, before the collected values are finally returned to the local context as the return value of the method invocation.
trans-unit.target: dRuby支持使用块调用远程方法。由于块（或代表它们的 Proc 对象）不可编组，因此该块在本地而不是远程上下文中执行。产生给该块的每个值都从远程对象传递到本地块，然后将每个块调用返回的值传递回要执行的远程执行上下文，然后才将收集到的值最终返回给本地上下文。方法调用的返回值。

trans-unit.source: destination_byteoffset and destination_bytesize specify the region which the converted result is stored. destination_byteoffset specifies the start position in destination_buffer in bytes. If destination_byteoffset is nil, destination_buffer.bytesize is used for appending the result. destination_bytesize specifies maximum number of bytes. If destination_bytesize is nil, destination size is unlimited. After conversion, destination_buffer is resized to destination_byteoffset + actually produced number of bytes. Also destination_buffer's encoding is set to destination_encoding.
trans-unit.target: destination_byteoffset和destination_bytesize指定了转换结果的存储区域。 destination_byteoffset指定了destination_buffer的起始位置,以字节为单位。如果 destination_byteoffset 为零,则使用 destination_buffer.bytesize 来追加结果。 destination_bytesize 指定最大的字节数。如果destination_bytesize为nil,则destination大小为无限大。转换后,destination_buffer的大小被调整为destination_byteoffset+实际产生的字节数。同时,destination_buffer的编码也被设置为destination_encoding。

trans-unit.source: destination_byteoffset should be an integer or nil. nil means the end of destination_buffer. If it is omitted, nil is assumed.
trans-unit.target: destination_byteoffset应该是一个整数或nil,nil表示destination_buffer的结束。如果省略,则假定为nil。

trans-unit.source: destination_bytesize should be an integer or nil. nil means unlimited. If it is omitted, nil is assumed.
trans-unit.target: destination_bytesize应该是一个整数或nil,nil表示无限制。如果省略,则假定为nil。
